[FILE:301:descriptions/desc.primary]
Hexedit view and edit files in hexadecimal or in ASCII. hexedit shows a
file both in ASCII and in hexadecimal. The file can be a device as the
file is not whole read. You can modify the file and search through it.
You have also copy&paste, and save to file functions. Modifications are
shown in bold.


